Mona Marshall https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mona_Marshall 0 Mona Iannotti, who goes by Mona Marshall, is an American voice actress known for her work in a number of cartoons, anime shows, films and video games. Her major credits include South Park, where she voices many of the female characters on the show; Fraggle Rock, CBS Storybreak, and Digimon. She has also appeared on-stage for television shows such as Cheers and Who's the Boss?
